quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  9,27,phir khuda is ke baad jis par chahay meharbani se tavajja farmaiye aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  9,28,momino! mushriq to palidh hain to is baras ke baad woh Khana kaaba ka paas nah jaane payen aur agar tum ko muflisi ka khauf ho to khuda chahay ga to tum ko apne fazl se ghanni kar day ga. be shak khuda sab kuch jaanta ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  9,29,jo ahal kitaab mein se khuda par imaan nahi laatay aur nah roz akhirat par ( yaqeen rakhtay hain ) aur nah un cheezon ko haraam samajte hain jo khuda aur is ke rasool ne haraam ki hain aur nah deen haq ko qubool karte hain un se jung karo yahan taq ke zaleel hokar apne haath se jaziya den
  9,30,aur yahood kehte hain ke uzair khuda ke betay hain aur isaai kehte hain ke maseeh khuda ke betay hain. yeh un ke munh ki baatein hain pehlay kafir bhi isi terhan ki baatein kaha karte they yeh bhi inhen ki race karne mein lagey hain. khuda un ko halaak kere. yeh kahan behke phirtay hain
  9,31,unhon ne apne ulama aur mashaiykh aur maseeh Ibn maryam ko allah ke siwa khuda bana liya halaank unn ko yeh hukum diya gaya tha ke khuday-e wahid ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karen. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. aur woh un logon ke shareek muqarrar karne se pak hai
